What is AI (Artificial Intelligence) ?
   =>     Artificial Intelligence (AI) is a field of computer science that focuses on   creating machines or software that can perform tasks which normally require human intelligence.


   In simple way we can say that :-
       =>  AI = machines that can think, learn, and make decisions like humans .


    Example of AI are :-
         Voice assistants (like Siri, Alexa)
         Chatbots (like ChatGPT)
         Recommendation systems (Netflix, YouTube)
         Self-driving cars
         Face recognition


    What can AI do ?
       => AI systems can:
                  Learn from data 📊
                  Understand language 💬
                  Recognize images 🖼️
                  Make decisions 🤔
                  Solve problems 🧩


    Types of AI :-
       1. Narrow AI (most common):-
            => Performs specific tasks only
               Example: Chatbots, Google Maps

       2. General AI (Future concept) :- 
            => Can perform any human-level task
               Still not fully developed


     How AI works ? 
          => AI uses :-
                 Algorithms
                 Data 
                 Models

                 It learns patterns from data and improves over time.


    Importance of AI :- 
       => AI helps in different ways 